<h1>Winter Schedule and Materials</h1>
<p>We will meet weekly to discuss new content, present current state of our projects, workshop new ideas, and play relevant games. There are readings each week that are mandatory, as well as some recommended additional readings that are optional. This schedule will change and evolve, in particular as project milestones come online, so be prepared for more work and deliverables to be added as we narrow in on specific project objectives.</p>
